{"type":"message","id":"cfc0e070","parentId":"331f14c9","timestamp":"2026-04-27T23:56:38.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到了当前技能的结构。现在我要开始执行完整的升级计划。让我按照以下顺序进行：\n\n1. 创建新的目录结构\n2. 创建规则引擎\n3. 创建分层扫描脚本\n4. 创建规则文件\n5. 创建意图一致性检查\n6. 创建结构化输出\n7. 创建白名单机制\n8. 更新主脚本\n9. 进行测试\n\n让我开始执行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我现在开始执行完整的 v5.0.0 升级。让我按步骤进行：\n\n## 🚀 开始升级 v5.0.0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dd15f9f81ea77aa1f91d80cf91e36","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill && mkdir -p rules config bin"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":1928,"output":229,"cacheRead":102144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104301,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777334195282,"responseId":"20260428075635412e98f5d0554c6d"}}
