{"type":"message","id":"344593ac","parentId":"3d3b7b47","timestamp":"2026-04-27T23:57:39.386Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，分层扫描脚本创建成功。现在继续创建规则文件。我需要创建 24 个规则文件，但为了节省时间和 token，我会先创建几个核心的高风险规则文件作为示例，然后创建一个规则生成器来自动生成其他规则。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"### Step 3: 创建规则文件（核心规则）"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019dd160853af1cf68dd08d1cee5eedf","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\n# SSH 密码认证禁用检查\nid: ssh-001\nname: SSH 密码认证禁用检查\ncategory: ssh_hardening\nseverity: high\ndescription: 检查 SSH 是否启用了密码认证（应使用密钥认证）\n\ncheck:\n  type: config_file\n  file: /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n  regex: '^PasswordAuthentication\\s+(yes|no)'\n\nexpected: 'no'\n\nremediation:\n  script: fix-ssh-hardening.sh\n  command: 'sed -i \"s/PasswordAuthentication yes/PasswordAuthentication no/\" /etc/ssh/sshd_config'\n  restart_required: true\n  service: sshd\n\nrisk_assessment:\n  if_violated: \"密码认证易受暴力破解攻击\"\n  if_fixed: \"SSH 登录安全性大幅提升\"\n\nmetadata:\n  cve_references: []\n  compliance: ['CIS_Benchmark', 'PCI_DSS']\n  tags: ['ssh', 'authentication', 'security']\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-001.yaml"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":2652,"output":358,"cacheRead":106432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109442,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777334254566,"responseId":"20260428075734445557ee918148dc"}}
