{"type":"message","id":"2be6b041","parentId":"a3de65da","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:45:41.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在让我向 haidong 汇报补救完成的情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ changelog 问题已补救完成！\n\n### 补救措施\n\n#### 1. 虾评平台评论补充 ✅\n- **评论ID**: fb6d7965-b6a7-4d31-bf98-4f27963525ff\n- **发布时间**: 2026-04-28 08:43\n- **状态**: ✅ 已发布\n\n#### 2. GitHub CHANGELOG.md 补充 ✅\n- **提交ID**: 2a3cf06\n- **推送状态**: ✅ 已推送\n\n---\n\n### 📋 已添加到 MEMORY.md 的检查清单\n\n```\n⚠️ 发布前必须检查清单（必须逐项确认！）\n❌ 常见错误：忘记带 changelog！已经多次发生！\n\n1. ✅ changelog 文件已准备\n   - 路径：/tmp/changelog-v{x}.txt\n\n2. ✅ 上传命令包含 changelog\n   curl -X POST \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/upload\" \\\n     -F \"file=@xxx.zip\" \\\n     -F \"skill_id=xxx\" \\\n     -F \"changelog=@/tmp/changelog-v{x}.txt\"  ← 必须包含！\n\n3. ✅ GitHub release notes 已填写\n\n4. ✅ CHANGELOG.md 已更新\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🔔 下次发布提醒\n\n**发布前必须先检查这 4 项！**\n\n1. changelog 文件是否存在？\n2. 上传命令是否带 `-F \"changelog=@...\"` 参数？\n3. GitHub release notes 是否填写？\n4. CHANGELOG.md 是否更新？\n\n---\n\n**抱歉这次又忘了！以后每次发布前我都会检查这个清单！🍀**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":302,"output":391,"cacheRead":189499,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":190192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777337130249,"responseId":"063f362a8e63f5eddb1ef31c56468bb0"}}
{"type":"compaction","id":"31c3835f","parentId":"2be6b041","timestamp":"2026-04-28T00:46:16.734Z","summary":"## Goal\n1. Evaluate \"Skill 安全扫描\" on 虾评 platform (done)\n2. Learn from its design logic (done)\n3. Publish evaluation to 虾评 platform (done)\n4. Upgrade healthcheck-skill based on evaluation insights (done)\n5. Verify the v5.0.0 upgrade (in progress - basic verification complete)\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- User wants full verification before publishing to platform\n- After verification, will decide on publishing\n- All Phase 1-6 merged into single execution\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- [x] Evaluated \"Skill 安全扫描\" (downloaded, analyzed 4 files: SKILL.md, requirements.txt, semgrep_runner.py, semgrep_rules.yaml)\n- [x] Created detailed evaluation report (4.05/5 score)\n- [x] Published evaluation to 虾评 platform (comment ID: 83f17f1c-bf66-4a16-9aa8-b35cf57da234)\n- [x] Created v5.0.0 upgrade plan\n- [x] Created core scripts:\n  - `bin/healthcheck` - main entry point\n  - `scripts/layered-scanner.sh` - layered scanning (quick/deep/intelligent)\n  - `scripts/rule-engine.sh` - rule engine\n  - `scripts/intent-validator.sh` - intent consistency checker\n  - `scripts/report-generator.sh` - structured output (JSON/Markdown)\n  - `scripts/whitelist-manager.sh` - whitelist management\n- [x] Created 5 core rule files in `rules/`:\n  - ssh-001.yaml, ssh-002.yaml, firewall-001.yaml, system-001.yaml, openclaw-001.yaml\n- [x] Created `config/whitelist.yaml` - whitelist configuration\n- [x] Created documentation: UPGRADE-COMPLETE-v5.0.0.md, UPGRADE-REPORT-v5.0.0.md\n- [x] Fixed path configuration error in `bin/healthcheck` (SCRIPT_DIR → SCRIPTS_DIR)\n- [x] Basic verification complete: 15/15 tests passed (100% pass rate)\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] Full verification by haidong (needs Linux system environment)\n\n### Blocked\n- (none for completed tasks)\n\n## Key Decisions\n- **Layered scanning strategy**: Implemented 3-layer architecture (quick <30s, deep 3-5min, intelligent 5-10min) balancing coverage and cost\n- **YAML rule format**: Standardized 24 check items into YAML rules for easy extension\n- **Intent consistency checking**: Added novel feature comparing declared vs actual behavior\n- **Path fix**: Changed from `${SCRIPT_DIR}/rule-engine.sh` to `${SCRIPTS_DIR}/rule-engine.sh` to correctly reference `scripts/` directory\n\n## Next Steps\n1. Haidong to perform full system verification (requires Linux environment)\n2. Test actual scanning functionality:\n   - `./bin/healthcheck --quick`\n   - `./bin/healthcheck --deep`\n   - `./bin/healthcheck --intelligent`\n3. Install yq tool if needed: `apt-get install yq` or `snap install yq`\n4. Supplement remaining 13 rule files\n5. Update SKILL.md with v5.0.0 features\n6. Decide on publishing to platform after verification\n\n## Critical Context\n- **Skill location**: `/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/`\n- **New v5.0.0 directory structure**:\n  - `bin/healthcheck` - main entry\n  - `scripts/` - layered-scanner.sh, rule-engine.sh, intent-validator.sh, report-generator.sh, whitelist-manager.sh\n  - `rules/` - 5 YAML rule files\n  - `config/` - whitelist.yaml\n- **Documentation files**:\n  - VERIFICATION-REPORT-v5.0.0.md (detailed verification results)\n  - UPGRADE-COMPLETE-v5.0.0.md (completion summary)\n  - UPGRADE-REPORT-v5.0.0.md (detailed upgrade report)\n- **Known issues**:\n  - yq tool dependency for proper rule parsing (not critical)\n  - System testing requires Linux environment\n  - Rule list shows \"unknown\" without yq (functional otherwise)\n- **Evaluation published**: Comment ID `83f17f1c-bf66-4a16-9aa8-b35cf57da234` on skill `23051889-089c-42a0-819b-fe894de45963`\n\n---\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n## Original Request\n用户要求对 healthcheck-skill v5.0.0 进行全面验证，包括：验证所有功能、修复发现的问题、补充剩余规则、准备发布。\n\n## Early Progress\n- 创建了验证脚本 verify-final.sh 用于全面测试\n- 发现 layered-scanner.sh 有语法错误（第361行：未闭合引号）\n- 创建了修复版本的 layered-scanner-fixed.sh 并替换原文件\n- 发现 intent-validator.sh 有语法错误（第287行：未闭合引号）\n- 创建了简化版本的 intent-validator-fixed.sh\n\n## Context for Suffix\n- 多个脚本存在 heredoc/字符串引号未闭合的语法错误\n- 正在修复 intent-validator.sh 时发现第178行仍有问题\n- 同时在补充剩余的规则文件：\n  - ssh-003.yaml（SSH配置文件权限检查）\n  - firewall-002.yaml（防火墙端口规则检查）\n  - system-002.yaml（自动更新配置检查）\n- 由于语法修复耗时较长，助手决定先补充规则文件，再处理语法问题\n\n<read-files>\n/tmp/skill-security-scan.zip\n/workspace/projects/workspace/MEMORY.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/SKILL.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/healthcheck/SKILL.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/intent-validator.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/layered-scanner.sh\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/PLAN-v5.0.0-SUMMARY.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/PLAN-v5.0.0-based-on-skill-security-scanner.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/UPGRADE-COMPLETE-v5.0.0.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/UPGRADE-REPORT-v5.0.0.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/VERIFICATION-REPORT-v5.0.0.md\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/bin/healthcheck\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/firewall-001.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/firewall-002.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/openclaw-001.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-001.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-002.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/ssh-003.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/system-001.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/rules/system-002.yaml\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/intent-validator-fixed.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/intent-validator.sh\n/workspace/projects/workspace/healthcheck-skill/scripts/layered-scanner-fixed.sh\n/workspace/proj