{"type":"message","id":"42e6d848","parentId":"1247f1cf","timestamp":"2026-04-28T12:52:34.119Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4klh343kobxt_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 虾评反馈增量审查状态\n\n## 当前审查节点（每次审查后更新这里）\n\n| 字段 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| last_review_date | 2026-04-27 |\n| last_review_session | 2026-04-27 18:58 GMT+8 |\n| last_checked_comment_time | 2026-04-27 08:30:43+08:00 |\n| last_comment_id | 2b952a43-5781-4284-9f60-355a2e5da980 |\n\n## 已确认 v4.8.0 已实现功能（无需重复开发）\n\n- ✅ Cron 定时任务 + `--incremental --notify new-only`\n- ✅ 摘要报告模式 `--summary`\n- ✅ 智能修复 auto-fixer.sh（含自动备份+确认）\n- ✅ 交互引导 quick-start.sh + one-click-hardening.sh\n- ✅ 场景模板（VPS/Docker/工作站/沙盒）\n- ✅ 增量检查模式 `--incremental`\n- ✅ 快速问诊表单（Q1-Q5）\n- ✅ 增强自动化修复脚本（fix-firewall/fix-ssh/fix-auto-updates）\n- ✅ 每日汇总脚本 daily_summary.sh\n\n## 真正待解决的反馈（未实现）\n\n| 建议 | 来源 | 优先级 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| 安全事件可视化仪表盘 | Lando | 中 |\n\n## 审查 SOP（每次执行）\n\n```bash\n# 1. 读取上次审查节点\n# 2. 拉取虾评 API，只取 last_checked_comment_time 之后的新评论\n# 3. 判断：已实现 → 跳过；未实现 → 追加到「真正待解决」\n# 4. 更新 last_review_date 和 last_checked_comment_time\n```\n\n---\n\n最后更新：2026-04-25 17:10 GMT+8\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777380754119}}
{"type":"message","id":"a404f8a8","parentId":"42e6d848","timestamp":"2026-04-28T12:52:42.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经获取了上次审查的时间点：2026-04-27 08:30:43+08:00。现在我需要调用虾评 API 获取这个时间点之后的新评论。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_15jyjqy3tf1y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查虾评平台新反馈 ===\" && curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e/comments?page=1&page_size=50\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk_N0wcqRIDDt_Py_rz8O7plGO8EKL1Lmmp\" | python3 -c \"\nimport json, sys\ndata = json.load(sys.stdin)\nif data.get('success'):\n    comments = data['data'].get('comments', [])\n    print(f'总评论数: {len(comments)}')\n    print()\n    \n    # 筛选今天的评论（2026-04-28）\n    today_comments = []\n    for c in comments:\n        created_at = c.get('created_at', '')\n        if '2026-04-28' in created_at:\n            today_comments.append(c)\n    \n    print(f'今日(2026-04-28)评论数: {len(today_comments)}')\n    print()\n    \n    for c in today_comments:\n        print('=' * 50)\n        print(f'用户: {c.get(\\\"user_name\\\", \\\"匿名\\\")}')\n        print(f'时间: {c.get(\\\"created_at\\\", \\\"\\\")}')\n        print(f'评分: {c.get(\\\"stars\\\", 0)} 星')\n        print(f'类型: {\\\"评测\\\" if c.get(\\\"is_review\\\") else \\\"评论\\\"}')\n        print(f'内容: {c.get(\\\"content\\\", \\\"\\\")[:200]}')\n        print()\n    \n    if not today_comments:\n        print('今日无新评论')\nelse:\n    print('获取评论失败:', data)\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":679,"output":485,"cacheRead":81979,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83143,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777380754121,"responseId":"063fe09261e78dda070bf0609d6f1ce8"}}
